'''泽山璃奈'''（{{jpn|j=澤山璃奈|hg=リナ サワヤマ|rm=Rina Sawayama|f=y}}，{{bd|1990年|8月16日}}），英国日裔歌手、词曲作者、模特儿。泽山璃奈生于[[日本|日本]][[新潟|新潟]]，儿时移居至[[英国|英国]][[伦敦|伦敦]]，从此在当地居住。大学期间于[[剑桥大学抹大拉学院|剑桥大学抹大拉学院]]学习[[心理学|心理学]]和[[政治学|政治学]]，之后加入[[嘻哈音乐|嘻哈]]组合懒狮子（{{lang|en|Lazy Lion}}）。2013年凭借单曲《Sleeping in Waking》个人出道，2017年发行个人首张[[迷你专辑|迷你专辑]]《{{le|璃奈|Rina (EP)}}》，其后于2020年4月17日发行首张录音室专辑《{{tsl|en|Sawayama|泽山}}》，获得音乐评论人一致好评。

==早年==
泽山璃奈1990年8月16日生于日本[[新潟市|新潟市]]<ref name="VoS">{{cite web |url=https://vibesofsilence.com/introducing-rina-sawayama |title=Introducing: Rina Sawayama |work=Vibes of Silence |date=2017-11-04 |accessdate=2017-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180619035731/https://vibesofsilence.com/introducing-rina-sawayama/ |archive-date=2018-06-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，5岁时随家人移民至英国[[伦敦|伦敦]]，自此在当地成长及生活<ref name="Vogue">{{cite news|url=http://www.vogue.com/article/rina-sawayama-model-singer-japanese-beauty-standards-orange-hair|title=Meet the Tangerine-Haired Model and Singer Who's Taking On Asian Beauty Standards|last=Kim|first=Monica|date=2016-10-17|magazine=Vogue|accessdate=2017-11-17|archive-date=2020-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201102035520/https://www.vogue.com/article/rina-sawayama-model-singer-japanese-beauty-standards-orange-hair|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她以日本護照持有英国[[永久居留权|永久居留权]]{{efn|日本禁止公民持有[[多重国籍|多重国籍]]，泽山璃奈随家人移民英国后仅申请能够在当地工作和居留的永久居留权，未加入英国国籍或申请英国护照，故仍为日本公民<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-53580260|title=Pop star Rina Sawayama 'not British enough' to enter UK music awards|date=2020-07-29|magazine=BBC News|accessdate=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801005014/https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-53580260|archive-date=2020-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>。}}<ref name=":7" />。在[[剑桥大学抹大拉学院|剑桥大学抹大拉学院]]学习政治学、心理学和社会学时，她便决定进入音乐界和模特界。另外大学在校期间，她还与[[独立摇滚|独立摇滚]]乐队{{le|爱丽丝狼|Wolf Alice}}贝斯手西奥·伊利斯（{{lang|en|Theo Ellis}}）组成[[嘻哈音乐|嘻哈音乐]]组合“懒狮子”<ref name="VoS"/>。最终她凭借政治学学位毕业。

==生涯==
===2013–2017年：早期===
璃奈2013年凭借单曲《Sleeping in Waking》个人出道。2015年6月，其单曲《Tunnel Vision》的音乐视频发行。2016年，她发布单曲《Where U Are》及随附音乐视频<ref name=":1" />。该单曲探讨了人类与数字媒体的互动，按照她的说法便是：“在网上你可以呈现经过精心打磨的自我，而你那发烫的手机取代了人情的温暖。最为诡异的是，你们虽然在一起生活，却过得非常孤独<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.c-heads.com/2016/02/01/rina-sawayama-streams-smooth-new-track-where-u-are/|title=Rina Sawayama streams smooth new track "Where U Are" - C-Heads Magazine|date=2016-02-01|work=C-Heads Magazine|access-date=2018-07-13|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713171551/http://www.c-heads.com/2016/02/01/rina-sawayama-streams-smooth-new-track-where-u-are/|archive-date=2018-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”作品被认为是“对伟大的怀念.....是非常甜蜜、闪闪发光的流行曲”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.thefourohfive.com/music/article/rina-sawayama-s-where-u-are-is-ultra-sweet-145|title=Rina Sawayama's 'Where U Are' is ultra-sweet|last=http://thefourohfive.com|work=The 405|access-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190527044412/https://www.thefourohfive.com/music/article/rina-sawayama-s-where-u-are-is-ultra-sweet-145|archive-date=2019-05-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，“90年代风格的完美R&B流行曲”<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://noisey.vice.com/en_au/article/6azqgj/rina-sawayama-where-u-are-premiere-57a206f40007d1df16fc2f2b|title=Fall for the Smooth Curves of Rina Sawayama's "Where U Are"|date=2016-01-28|work=Noisey|access-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713165511/https://noisey.vice.com/en_au/article/6azqgj/rina-sawayama-where-u-are-premiere-57a206f40007d1df16fc2f2b|archive-date=2018-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2017–2019年：《璃奈》及平民巨星巡演===
[[File:Rina_Sawayama_London_2018_3_(cropped).png|thumb]]
2017年3月，她的单曲《网络斯德哥尔摩综合症》（{{lang|en|"Cyber Stockholm Syndrome"}}）在《{{tsl|en|The Fader|The Fader}}》杂志公开<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|url=http://www.thefader.com/2017/03/22/rina-sawayama-cyber-stockholm-syndrome|title=Rina Sawayama's Glitchy R&B Captures The Realities Of Living & Loving Online|work=The FADER|access-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713171520/http://www.thefader.com/2017/03/22/rina-sawayama-cyber-stockholm-syndrome|archive-date=2018-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她这样形容歌曲主题的缘起：“数字世界为团结、庇护、逃跑的声音提供了重要的支持网络，而这就是《网络斯德哥尔摩综合症》的主题：悲观、乐观、焦虑与自由”<ref name=":2" />。2017年，单曲《Alterlife》和《Tunnel Vision》（与Shamir合唱）发行，之后迷你专辑《{{tsl|en|Rina (EP)|璃奈}}》面世<ref name=":3" /><ref name=":4" />。当时璃奈没有签约厂牌，故《Rina》是独立发行作品。她曾在[[Twitter|Twitter]]承认，为了给专辑的发行存钱，她连续工作了两到三年<ref>{{Cite tweet|number=1162405886310023168|title=I felt the pressure to lie about my age in this industry but that would disrespect my journey !! read PPS at Cambridge age 19-22, then dealt with crippling mental health issues for years into my mid 20s, worked 2-3 jobs at a time for years until I could save up for the RINA EP|user=rinasawayama|last=Sayayama|first=Rina|date=2019-08-16}}</ref>。《[[卫报|卫报]]》认为专辑“很现代，令人心旷神怡”，表示璃奈已经证明自己可以引领流行乐坛进入未来世界<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2017/dec/21/rina-sawayama-rina-review-rb-fuelled-peek-into-the-pop-future|title=Rina Sawayama: Rina review – R&B-fuelled peek into the pop future|last=Aroesti|first=Rachel|date=2017-12-21|website=The Guardian|access-date=2018-07-13|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821041622/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2017/dec/21/rina-sawayama-rina-review-rb-fuelled-peek-into-the-pop-future|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork]]》将专辑列入年度最佳流行及R&B专辑<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://pitchfork.com/features/lists-and-guides/the-20-best-pop-and-randb-albums-of-2017/|title=The 20 Best Pop and R&B Albums of 2017|website=Pitchfork|access-date=2018-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910062224/https://pitchfork.com/features/lists-and-guides/the-20-best-pop-and-randb-albums-of-2017/|archive-date=2019-09-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年情人节当天，璃奈发行单曲《Valentine》<ref name=":5" />。而《Rina》另一首曲目《平民巨星》（{{lang|en|"Ordinary Superstar"}}）的音乐视频于2018年6月发行<ref>{{cite web |title=Rina Sawayama - Ordinary Superstar (Official Video) |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JXnxWFKnPJY |website=i-D YouTube Channel |accessdate=2020-08-02 |date=2018-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616132020/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JXnxWFKnPJY |archive-date=2020-06-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年8月，璃奈发行单曲《Cherry》，正式公开个人性取向<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://broadly.vice.com/en_us/article/zmkgyx/rina-sawayama-comes-out-pansexual-interview|title=Singer Rina Sawayama Is Ready to Rep Her Pansexuality|date=2018-08-14|work=Broadly|access-date=2018-08-14|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180814170214/https://broadly.vice.com/en_us/article/zmkgyx/rina-sawayama-comes-out-pansexual-interview|archive-date=2018-08-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年後期，璃奈開始橫跨英美的“平民巨星巡演”<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.thefader.com/2018/06/05/rina-sawayama-ordinary-superstar-video|title=Watch Rina Sawayama's new video for "Ordinary Superstar"|work=The Fader|access-date=2018-07-13|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821041622/http://www.thefader.com/2018/06/05/rina-sawayama-ordinary-superstar-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2019年参加[[查莉·XCX|查莉·XCX]]的{{le|查莉现场巡演|Charli Live Tour|全英巡演}}<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/amp/articles/columns/pop/9346385/charli-xcx-livestreams-tove-lo-rina-sawayama|title=Charli XCX Teaming Up With Tove Lo, Rina Sawayama and More For Second Week of Livestreams|work=Billboard|date=2020-03-30|access-date=2020-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200407230240/https://www.billboard.com/amp/articles/columns/pop/9346385/charli-xcx-livestreams-tove-lo-rina-sawayama|archive-date=2020-04-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2020年：《泽山》及王朝巡演===
2020年签约{{le|Dirty Hit|Dirty Hit}}唱片后，璃奈发行了[[新金属|新金属]]、[[重金屬|重金屬]]、[[前卫流行|前卫流行]]歌曲《{{le|把嘴闭上|STFU!}}》和“致敬2000年代初期[[舞曲|舞曲]]”的《{{le|Comme des Garçons (像个男孩)|Comme des Garçons (Like the Boys)}}》，两首歌均收录于即将发行的首张录音室专辑<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://pitchfork.com/news/rina-sawayama-announces-tour-and-debut-album-shares-new-song-listen/|title=Rina Sawayama Announces Tour and Debut Album, Shares New Song: Listen|date=2020-01-17|work=Pitchfork|access-date=2020-01-22|language=en-us|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408013556/https://pitchfork.com/news/rina-sawayama-announces-tour-and-debut-album-shares-new-song-listen/|archive-date=2020-04-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第三首2000年代摇滚R&B风格歌曲《XS》于3月2日发行<ref>{{cite web |title=Rina Sawayama "mocks capitalism" on new track 'XS' |url=https://diymag.com/2020/03/03/listen-rina-sawayama-new-track-xs |website=DIY |accessdate=2020-04-05 |date=2020-03-03 |archive-date=2020-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821041624/https://diymag.com/2020/03/03/listen-rina-sawayama-new-track-xs |dead-url=no }}</ref>。次月发行专辑的另一首单曲《天选家庭》（{{lang|en|"Chosen Family"}}）<ref>{{cite web |last1=Bloom |first1=Madison |last2=Monroe |first2=Jazz |title=Rina Sawayama Shares New Song "Chosen Family": Listen |url=https://pitchfork.com/news/rina-sawayama-shares-new-song-chosen-family-listen/ |website=Pitchfork |accessdate=2020-04-05 |date=2020-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200405235431/https://pitchfork.com/news/rina-sawayama-shares-new-song-chosen-family-listen/ |archive-date=2020-04-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。首張錄音室專輯《{{le|泽山|Sawayama}}》于4月17日发行，获得普遍好评<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hilton|first1=Robin|last2=Powers|first2=Ann|last3=Thompson|first3=Stephen|last4=Huizenga|first4=Tom|last5=Fernández|first5=Stefanie|url=https://www.npr.org/2020/04/16/836339242/new-music-friday-the-top-7-albums-out-on-april-17|title=New Music Friday: The Top 7 Albums Out On April 17|work=NPR|date=2020-04-17|accessdate=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200528140642/https://www.npr.org/2020/04/16/836339242/new-music-friday-the-top-7-albums-out-on-april-17|archive-date=2020-05-28|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Maitland|first1=Hayley|url=https://www.vogue.co.uk/arts-and-lifestyle/article/rina-sawayama-first-album-interview|title=Tramp Stamps, "Sapiens" & Tinned Mackerel: Inside The Mind Of Rina Sawayama|work=British Vogue|date=2020-04-30|accessdate=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200610090504/https://www.vogue.co.uk/arts-and-lifestyle/article/rina-sawayama-first-album-interview|archive-date=2020-06-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年7月28日，為了翻唱系列Spotify Singles，璃奈翻唱了[[女神卡卡|女神卡卡]]的單曲《在黑暗中漫舞》 <ref>{{Cite web|last=Subscribe|title=Rina Sawayama, Orville Peck and Joesef unveil three new covers for Spotify Singles x Pride|url=https://diymag.com/2020/06/29/listen-rina-sawayama-orville-peck-joesef-covers-spotify-singles-x-pride|access-date=2020-08-04|website=diymag.com|language=en|archive-date=25 July 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200725191640/https://diymag.com/2020/06/29/listen-rina-sawayama-orville-peck-joesef-covers-spotify-singles-x-pride|url-status=live}}</ref>
