== 其他事业 ==

===模特生涯===
泽山一直以来是非主流经纪公司Anti Agency和{{le|Elite模特經紀公司|Elite Model Management}}的签约模特儿。2017年，她获邀参加[[范思哲|范思哲]]{{tsl|en|Versus (Versace)|Versus (范思哲)|Versus x Versace}}秋冬季宣传<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/style/article/rina-sawayama-beauty/index.html|title=Pop singer Rina Sawayama says 'STFU!' to stereotypes|last=Bateman|first=Hilary Whiteman, CNN {{!}} Kristen|website=CNN|language=en|access-date=2020-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200423081556/https://www.cnn.com/style/article/rina-sawayama-beauty/index.html|archive-date=2020-04-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>，另外还参与了[[卓丹·鄧|卓丹·鄧]]“Missguided”系列宣传片的拍摄<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/people/jourdan-dunn-empowering-new-collection-supermodel-really-wears/|title=Jourdan Dunn on her empowering new collection - and what a supermodel really wears on the school run|last=Holt|first=Bethan|date=2017-03-10|work=The Telegraph|access-date=2018-07-13|language=en-GB|issn=0307-1235|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713181834/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/fashion/people/jourdan-dunn-empowering-new-collection-supermodel-really-wears/|archive-date=2018-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并為{{tsl|en|Nicola Formichetti|尼古拉·福米切蒂}}MAC x Nicopanda联名系列创作了原聲歌曲<ref>{{cite web |last1=Moran |first1=Justin |title=MAC Collabs with Nicola Formichetti on Nicopanda Makeup |url=https://www.papermag.com/mac-nicopanda-2540857965.html |website=Paper |accessdate=2020-08-02 |date=2018-02-28 |archive-date=2018-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180228184321/https://www.papermag.com/mac-nicopanda-2540857965.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===跨界合作===
2016年，璃奈与台湾视觉艺术家[[江宥儀|江宥儀]]进行合作，拍攝了一系列批判亚洲和日本人的审美标准的視覺作品。随后她登上《[[时尚_(Vogue)|时尚]]》杂志。璃奈在采访中表示，这次的合作之所以存在，是因为“對日本女性來說，從动漫到卡哇伊文化中的元素都是社会对她们的期待......这种局面实际上将女性置于不利的地位，被人物化和婴儿化”<ref name="Vogue" />。 璃奈曾与尼古拉·福米切蒂在[[MAC_(化妆品)|MAC]] x Nicopanda联名系列中合作。福米切蒂还执导了璃奈歌曲《平民巨星》的音乐视频，並在“i-D”网站讲述了两人合作的起因<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://i-d.vice.com/en_uk/article/a3aj9j/read-rina-sawayama-and-nicola-formichettis-texts-to-each-other|title=read rina sawayama and nicola formichetti's texts to each other|date=2018-06-05|work=I-d|access-date=2018-07-13|language=en-GB|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180713165701/https://i-d.vice.com/en_uk/article/a3aj9j/read-rina-sawayama-and-nicola-formichettis-texts-to-each-other|archive-date=2018-07-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

